Package: copulary
Title: Create and Evaluate Bivariate Copulas
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Vincenzo", "Coia", "vcoia@bgcengineering.ca", 
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Mariia", "Morello", role = "ctb")
    )
Description: Make bivariate copula objects 
    (of class "cop"). Evaluate their properties, such as density,
    cdf, mass, mean, variance, etc., and generate random
    observations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    tibble
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: 
    rlang,
    stats,
    vctrs
Depends: 
    igcop
